{"tid":2489882,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【2021年】【0415 LIVE】衞生署及醫管局4點半疫情簡報會","createTime":"2021-04-15T08:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T08:27:59.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"98bf41393f4dfa58e23985dc0909d2458af7a98a","tid":2489882,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:25:02.000Z","msg":"<strong>是日出席代表：食物及衞生局副局長徐德義、衞生署衞生防護中心傳染病處高級醫生王智康、醫院管理局總行政經理（質素及標準）劉家獻</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1584e8e1ab547e67c58c29fb99642457135e2f29","tid":2489882,"uid":365024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:25:06.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"c2fc943fb548104db5f7fad8f9631d974097a64c","tid":2489882,"uid":244704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:25:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k19ii3QYH8w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dk19ii3QYH8w&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=70647a59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k19ii3QYH8w</a>"},{"pid":"b16223994e115a2098a13df298e7fe6598bcfd69","tid":2489882,"uid":260251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:25:09.000Z","msg":"N"},{"pid":"278751010ef1d5b03e7676916638d5191cec85d1","tid":2489882,"uid":200343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ca0410ae7f2c45f28186985374e8b9b187c4fe","tid":2489882,"uid":246731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce0405de7dadaceb7c51e71b00b81c18c943f60","tid":2489882,"uid":308558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6df48dc15e6339b2b524b1054c8250590ef0842","tid":2489882,"uid":93600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714f70a607b5dc9bfcee98854f49e1e2dcd05216","tid":2489882,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:25:25.000Z","msg":"<strong>599J強制檢測途徑：</strong><br />\n（一）於流動採樣站接受檢測服務（名單及服務對象：<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fearly-testing.html&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=052e7f09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html</a>）[中資]<br />\n（二）於社區檢測中心接受檢測服務（名單：<a href=\"http://www.communitytest.gov.hk/zh-HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.communitytest.gov.hk%2Fzh-HK%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=02426ff8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.communitytest.gov.hk/zh-HK/</a>）[中資]<br />\n（三）於121間郵政局、20個港鐵站設置的自動派發機或醫院管理局47間指定普通科門診診所索取深喉唾液測試樣本收集包，並把樣本交回指定樣本收集點（派發點及時間，以及樣本收集點及時間：<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fearly-testing.html&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=052e7f09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html</a>）[難確定，或有中資]<br />\n（四）於醫管局普通科門診診所按照醫管局醫護人員的指示接受檢測<br />\n（五）自行安排接受由衞生署認可，並可就檢測結果發出電話短訊通知的私營化驗所提供的檢測（名單：<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/List_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2FList_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=2bd6199f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/List_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf</a>）<br />\n（六）使用衞生防護中心派發到相關指明地方的樣本瓶（如適用），並按有關指示交回已採樣本的檢測樣本收集瓶。"},{"pid":"31f297da6992e5f885e314b00cc15f753ff127e7","tid":2489882,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1584e8e1ab547e67c58c29fb99642457135e2f29","tid":2489882,"uid":365024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:25:06.000Z","msg":"Hi"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be900004edfe2b6065c6f10f35bce8415549b764","tid":2489882,"uid":93600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:25:38.000Z","msg":"more than 1 unlink<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73a4eb679f1cf3e81111d0a7a14cacc05145343","tid":2489882,"uid":47697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:25:41.000Z","msg":"h"},{"pid":"ec7e8a4c50797506d94e8ffab83e776e014b0da5","tid":2489882,"uid":93600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b16223994e115a2098a13df298e7fe6598bcfd69","tid":2489882,"uid":